From a7fc27c50888e24886c23453ea43eaaa95906f59 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Enrique Parodi Spalazzi <enrique.parodi@airbus.com>
Date: Sun, 26 Apr 2026 02:13:38 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 1/4] feat[installer]: add curl|sh quick installer

Single-file POSIX sh installer that drops a Sen release build into
$HOME/.sen/<build-id>/ and writes activate scripts (bash/zsh and fish
native) for the user to source. Patterned after rustup / starship; no
Conan, no sudo, Linux only.

Includes 67 bats tests covering parse, URL resolution, install pipeline,
and generated activate scripts under bash/dash/zsh/fish, plus a GitHub
Actions workflow and a pre-commit hook gated on changes under
resources/installer/.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 <noreply@anthropic.com>
