--- a/.conan/profiles/sen_clang
+++ b/.conan/profiles/sen_clang
@@ -1,6 +1,12 @@
+# CI baseline profile for Linux + clang 20. Architecture is intentionally not pinned so the same profile
+# resolves on x86_64 CI runners and on aarch64 dev hosts. On a non-Linux host, prefer `conan profile detect`
+# instead of this profile. The system_package_manager conf assumes the runner has root privileges and no sudo
+# (as in the CI image and the docker dev container); on a workstation, either pre-install libxext-dev or
+# override `sudo` on the conan command line.
+
